structure.unit: PAYMENT, COLLECTION, AND REFUND OF TAXES

law.history: Repealed 2009 Ky. Acts ch. 10, sec. 71, effective January 1, 2010. -- Amended 2006 Ky. Acts ch. 252, Pt. XXVIII, sec. 15, effective April 25, 2006. -- Amended 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 85, sec. 252, effective June 20, 2005. -- Amended 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 264, sec. 5, effective July 15, 1982. -- Created 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 240, sec. 2, effective July 15, 1980.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Clerk to file lien for taxes on motor vehicles or trailers -- Accounting by clerk of payments received.
